videos.description: Jumpstarted by senior John Petty Jr., who shot 8-of-10 from deep, No. 18 Alabama cruises past LSU 105-75 and breaks its own SEC single-game 3-point record.
videos.headline: Bama breaks its own SEC record for 3-pointers with 23
